            <title>从《极简欧洲史》看竞技精神：逆转背后的文明基因与体育传承</title>
            <link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E4%BB%8E%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%80%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%8F%B2%E7%9C%8B%E7%AB%9E%E6%8A%80%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%86%E8%BD%AC%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E4%BC%A0%E6%89%BF/</link>
